cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper discusses the fundamental mechanisms of autonomous development and learning in artificial intelligence and robotics, which are related to the fields of AI, robotics, machine learning, and neural networks. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also discusses the integration of deep learning with other mechanisms such as curiosity, social learning, and embodiment, which are related to the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
